milestones.description: This is the lowest match aggregate (376) involving teams Zimbabwe & Bangladesh in ODIs
Zimbabwe's 193-run win against Bangladesh is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 131-run win against England
Khaled Mashud has broken the record for most dismissals in an innings (4) in ODIs for BAN, going past Khaled Mashud's 2
